{"word":"H8034 - שֵׁם - shêm - shame - Base","slug":"H8034","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שֵׁם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shêm"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shame"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Base"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DD; - she&#x0302;m</b> - <i>shame</i><p/>A primitive word (perhaps rather from <a href=\"#/H7760\">H7760</a> through the idea of definite and conspicuous <i>position</i>; compare <a href=\"#/H8064\">H8064</a>); an <i>appellation</i>, as a mark or memorial of individuality; by implication <i>honor</i>, <i>authority</i>, <i>character: - </i> + base, [in-] fame [-ous], name (-d), renown, report."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3074\">H3074</a>, <a href=\"#/H8033\">H8033</a>, <a href=\"#/H8035\">H8035</a>, <a href=\"#/H8038\">H8038</a>, <a href=\"#/H8050\">H8050</a>, <a href=\"#/H8061\">H8061</a>, <a href=\"#/H8062\">H8062</a>, <a href=\"#/H8070\">H8070</a>"}]}